description: Welcome to 150 W Broadway—a modern 2 bed, 1.5 bath unit offering 1000 square feet of stylish living in the heart of South Boston. Built in 2018, this home features wide-plank hardwood floors, a chef’s kitchen with quartz waterfall island, custom blinds, and oversized windows flooding the space with natural light. The spacious primary suite includes a walk-in closet and spa-like bath, while the second bedroom offers flexibility for guests or a home office. Enjoy a private balcony, heated bathroom floors, in-unit laundry, and a deeded garage parking spot. Building amenities include a shared roof deck with gas grill, elevator, and professional management—all just steps from the Broadway T, Seaport, South End, and top local dining & shopping.
